{"about_the_game":"<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/mid_world_map_8_player.gif?t=1733400118\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">CASE is a <strong>turn-based strategy</strong> game that can be played with up to 8 players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your main objective is to ally with one other player and eliminate all enemies from the map.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You start the game with a chosen tile and complete your base on the map during the peace phase.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can place pickaxes and shields on your tiles for production and defense, which can be upgraded up to 3 levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/mid_pickaxe_shield_place.gif?t=1733400118\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you expand across the map, you have a chance to find various unique cards; using these cards strategically is entirely up to you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Development cards</strong> help you grow faster.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/mid_upgrade_card.gif?t=1733400118\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Attack cards</strong> allow you to fight against your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/mid_attack_card.gif?t=1733400118\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Trap cards</strong> catch enemies by surprise if they try to conquer you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/mid_trap_card.gif?t=1733400118\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Political cards</strong> give you the power to interfere with other players' strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/mid_politic_card.gif?t=1733400118\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remember, in CASE, nothing is bad if you're winning in the end. Join the battlefield and fight against your enemies!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Use Card 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098580/b98be44cfe276363b7acdc3f2542865d77cbd5a3.jpg"},{"name":"Use Card 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098580/e126e67e16ec3aa56d1ca3c829389421cdbae216.jpg"},{"name":"Use Card 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098580/81cbb18a95ddbc7dfb8012775920ee9b1b5db7e2.jpg"},{"name":"Conquer 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098580/b099c02fb7b5335a593e31790da49c193eda1546.jpg"},{"name":"Conquer 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098580/0e6dae5e72c623bfe0f2872901088bebc2d9de99.jpg"},{"name":"Conquer 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098580/d5513194e9b8d5ba3f6cc1faf5c50d94ca899d53.jpg"},{"name":"Attack! 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098580/d62cfbd8261bfd6d0ada6573acd00cadf817f933.jpg"},{"name":"Attack! 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098580/f9f4eb1a050474ba004e3f3be50daa3104fb85c1.jpg"},{"name":"Attack! 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098580/3e6c6b5ace16177fb9248c5bef17caa2e0812397.jpg"},{"name":"Social 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/im